WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 32]

01:16.750 --> 01:17.650
Come check Lifei out.

01:31.520 --> 01:32.730
Her meridians are reconnected.

01:41.360 --> 01:41.890
Lifei.

01:52.910 --> 01:54.780
Why did you give me your cultivation?

01:56.550 --> 01:58.220
We're already advanced in years.

01:58.470 --> 01:59.530
The spirit energy

02:00.080 --> 02:00.940
is useless to us now.

02:06.600 --> 02:07.220
Elder Zhu.

02:08.520 --> 02:09.940
Don't dwell on that.

02:11.030 --> 02:11.780
Lifei,

02:12.080 --> 02:12.810
just go.

02:13.870 --> 02:14.410
Go?

02:15.360 --> 02:16.020
Where to?

02:33.830 --> 02:37.180
Has the mountain-sea barrier been broken?

02:40.520 --> 02:44.020
We can't escape this great calamity.

02:46.990 --> 02:50.810
The Sea Calamity came from the bloodshed of immortal sects.

02:51.430 --> 02:53.410
This sin is of our own making,

02:53.920 --> 02:55.970
and we must bear it ourselves.

02:57.710 --> 02:59.780
Leave this to us.

03:01.080 --> 03:01.850
Elder Zhu,

03:02.830 --> 03:04.690
do you also know the legend of the Sea Calamity?

03:08.200 --> 03:10.850
Years ago, to hunt for the Divine Tree,

03:11.480 --> 03:13.060
I pored over ancient scrolls in the Central Plains.

03:13.520 --> 03:15.130
One scroll recorded

03:15.710 --> 03:16.970
that 1,000 years ago,

03:17.040 --> 03:19.500
a woman who could absorb heaven and earth's spirit energy

03:19.520 --> 03:21.460
was slain by immortals in the East Sea.

03:22.670 --> 03:25.940
That marked the first arrival of the Sea Calamity.

03:26.550 --> 03:28.970
The Sea Calamity is divine retribution.

03:29.550 --> 03:30.810
We cannot abide anything

03:30.830 --> 03:32.570
different from us

03:32.590 --> 03:34.180
and seek only to destroy it.

03:38.920 --> 03:40.530
Our ignorance

03:41.150 --> 03:43.810
brought forth this calamity.

03:46.270 --> 03:47.620
That woman was the Divine Tree.

03:49.640 --> 03:51.130
The Divine Tree caused the Sea Calamity

03:51.990 --> 03:53.500
and shall end it.

03:58.590 --> 04:01.810
Lifei, you've been reborn as a human.

04:02.960 --> 04:04.410
You're no different from the rest of us.

04:05.240 --> 04:06.410
The immortal sects

04:07.920 --> 04:08.970
have wronged you.

04:19.480 --> 04:20.450
All things bear

04:21.350 --> 04:22.570
their karmic causes and fruits.

04:25.150 --> 04:27.100
This fate was never yours to carry.

04:27.590 --> 04:30.450
We will never let you sacrifice yourself.

04:33.560 --> 04:34.250
Just go.

04:35.150 --> 04:35.980
Return to Qingqiu.

05:04.320 --> 05:04.980
It's Xiuyuan!

05:05.960 --> 05:06.570
Lei!

05:55.960 --> 05:56.770
The world teeters on collapse.

05:57.030 --> 05:58.010
We must lay aside old grudges

05:58.030 --> 05:58.770
and stand united.

05:59.520 --> 06:01.660
Whether one person, one realm, one sect, one clan,

06:02.350 --> 06:04.300
or human, spirit, demon, or monster,

06:04.760 --> 06:05.770
all are living beings under heaven.

06:07.470 --> 06:08.500
We must join hands as one.

07:02.350 --> 07:02.890
Succeeded.

07:04.030 --> 07:04.740
The earth fire recedes!

07:28.230 --> 07:28.770
Lifei.

07:30.960 --> 07:31.620
Where's Lifei?

08:32.640 --> 08:33.100
Oh, no.

08:33.910 --> 08:34.500
We can't stop it.

09:09.870 --> 09:10.610
This time,

09:13.350 --> 09:14.850
you must not take it back.

09:18.680 --> 09:20.300
I've failed my father after all.

09:24.830 --> 09:26.060
We have no regrets about holding out

09:28.280 --> 09:29.210
till the very end.

09:35.400 --> 09:37.020
In the end, everything was a fleeting dream.

09:54.680 --> 09:55.810
It's better to stay far away

09:58.110 --> 09:58.850
as long as you live safely.

10:29.920 --> 10:32.880
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

10:33.000 --> 10:35.640
♪I'll never back down♪

10:36.470 --> 10:37.020
Lifei.

10:37.020 --> 10:39.040
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

10:39.040 --> 10:39.810
It's Lifei.

10:42.710 --> 10:43.300
Lifei.

10:43.300 --> 10:45.660
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

10:45.780 --> 10:47.110
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

10:47.110 --> 10:47.660
Lifei.

10:48.900 --> 10:53.580
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

10:53.740 --> 10:57.080
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

10:57.080 --> 10:57.570
Lifei.

10:58.100 --> 11:00.580
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

11:00.700 --> 11:06.220
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

11:06.520 --> 11:10.320
♪Let frost, snow and rain block the long stone steps♪

11:10.480 --> 11:12.640
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

11:12.920 --> 11:18.440
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

11:18.720 --> 11:25.680
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

11:25.680 --> 11:26.260
It's enough.

11:26.590 --> 11:27.140
I'll take you away.

11:34.160 --> 11:35.570
This is what I have to do.

11:35.800 --> 11:37.780
I saw the karmic cycle overseas

11:37.800 --> 11:39.300
that the death of the Divine Tree causes the Sea Calamity.

11:39.320 --> 11:40.810
The Sea Calamity destroys the world with spirit energy,

11:40.830 --> 11:42.420
while the Divine Tree is born to absorb spirit energy.

11:42.680 --> 11:43.780
The two are intertwined

11:44.080 --> 11:45.330
yet opposed.

11:45.350 --> 11:46.690
I only wish to spend my life

11:46.990 --> 11:49.020
shielding Xiaobangchui from this disaster.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.690
The Sea Calamity began because of me,

11:54.960 --> 11:56.260
so only I can end it.

11:59.110 --> 11:59.610
Very well.

12:00.800 --> 12:01.420
I'm with you.

12:04.510 --> 12:05.140
Xiuyuan.

12:05.160 --> 12:05.940
We made a vow

12:06.800 --> 12:07.540
to live together

12:08.350 --> 12:10.970
or perish side by side.

12:39.590 --> 12:40.090
Lifei!

12:59.830 --> 13:00.610
Master,

13:05.040 --> 13:07.140
Xiaobangchui and Little Yecha, whom you protected,

13:08.350 --> 13:09.940
can finally guard those

13:11.110 --> 13:13.210
on the Central Plains you cherished.

13:16.320 --> 13:16.810
Lifei!

14:34.840 --> 14:38.520
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

14:38.840 --> 14:41.340
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

14:41.800 --> 14:45.120
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

14:45.360 --> 14:47.560
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

14:48.600 --> 14:52.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

14:52.800 --> 14:55.160
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

14:55.760 --> 14:57.280
♪No calamity can rival♪

14:57.680 --> 15:00.720
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

15:02.800 --> 15:06.280
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

15:07.040 --> 15:09.280
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

15:09.720 --> 15:12.760
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

15:13.400 --> 15:15.680
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

15:16.480 --> 15:19.960
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

15:20.740 --> 15:23.020
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

15:23.540 --> 15:26.500
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

15:27.220 --> 15:29.420
♪Reign supreme♪

15:30.080 --> 15:33.160
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

15:57.200 --> 16:00.880
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

16:01.200 --> 16:03.700
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

16:04.160 --> 16:07.480
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

16:07.720 --> 16:09.920
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

16:10.960 --> 16:14.440
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

16:14.920 --> 16:15.540
Lifei.

16:15.540 --> 16:17.520
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

16:18.040 --> 16:18.570
No.

16:18.570 --> 16:19.640
♪No calamity can rival♪

16:20.440 --> 16:21.090
Lifei.

16:21.090 --> 16:23.080
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

16:25.220 --> 16:28.700
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

16:29.460 --> 16:31.700
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

16:32.140 --> 16:35.180
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

16:35.820 --> 16:38.100
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

16:38.900 --> 16:42.380
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

16:42.990 --> 16:45.270
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

16:45.790 --> 16:48.750
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

16:49.470 --> 16:51.670
♪Reign supreme♪

16:52.520 --> 16:55.360
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

17:16.600 --> 17:20.080
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

17:20.840 --> 17:23.080
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

17:23.520 --> 17:26.560
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

17:27.200 --> 17:29.480
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

17:30.280 --> 17:33.760
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

17:34.520 --> 17:36.800
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

17:37.320 --> 17:40.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

17:41.160 --> 17:43.360
♪Reign supreme♪

17:43.960 --> 17:47.490
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

17:48.160 --> 17:50.530
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

17:50.850 --> 17:54.050
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

17:54.650 --> 17:56.930
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

17:57.330 --> 17:58.920
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

17:58.920 --> 17:59.420
Lifei.

18:01.690 --> 18:04.090
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

18:04.530 --> 18:07.690
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

18:08.960 --> 18:09.660
Lifei.

18:09.660 --> 18:10.650
♪And falling petals♪

18:11.370 --> 18:15.640
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

18:15.640 --> 18:16.660
The immortal sects are far from perfect,

18:17.120 --> 18:20.050
yet the world holds countless warm moments,

18:20.360 --> 18:21.620
like clusters of tiny flames,

18:21.880 --> 18:23.770
chasing away loneliness and cold, bringing hope.

18:24.270 --> 18:25.250
Someday,

18:25.640 --> 18:27.450
this world will become what Master hoped for.

18:27.790 --> 18:28.530
I firmly believe

18:28.840 --> 18:30.050
that the day will come.

18:30.270 --> 18:31.730
This is the aspiration of my cultivation.

18:32.030 --> 18:33.940
My journey in the mortal world

18:34.200 --> 18:35.690
has no regrets or sorrows.

18:36.120 --> 18:39.580
Generations of brilliant souls

18:41.270 --> 18:42.580
roamed everywhere

18:43.360 --> 18:44.340
to quell the Sea Calamity.

18:45.990 --> 18:47.820
Now the calamity is finally ended,

18:48.310 --> 18:49.010
but none

18:51.680 --> 18:52.580
of them remain.

18:58.440 --> 18:59.770
Still, I trust the future

19:00.600 --> 19:02.210
will unfold just as they wished.

19:44.680 --> 19:45.290
Sir,

19:46.360 --> 19:47.210
a letter from Mr. Mo.

19:50.920 --> 19:52.290
He said the Sea Calamity has vanished,

19:52.750 --> 19:54.730
and Xiuyuan has sent demons back to their overseas homelands.

19:55.360 --> 19:55.940
Besides,

19:56.440 --> 19:57.820
the seaway from the Central Plains to overseas lands

19:58.200 --> 19:59.820
rises again after being lost for thousands of years.

20:01.440 --> 20:02.660
Perhaps the exchange between the Central Plains

20:04.030 --> 20:05.820
and the outer realms can be restored.

20:16.840 --> 20:18.820
Truly, only he and she could bring

20:19.960 --> 20:24.180
great changes and vitality to the Central Plains.

20:25.470 --> 20:25.970
Sir,

20:27.160 --> 20:28.580
the remnant spirits of Lifei and Xiuyuan

20:28.710 --> 20:30.250
were taken away by the Nine-Tailed Fox and Mr. Yan.

20:31.470 --> 20:32.580
Is there a chance

20:33.270 --> 20:34.210
that they're still alive?

20:39.960 --> 20:41.140
Heaven pities all living beings.

20:41.710 --> 20:44.580
Kind hearts and good deeds shall reap good karma.

20:45.310 --> 20:46.010
There may be

20:48.160 --> 20:50.010
a glimmer of hope for them.

21:02.360 --> 21:03.420
A decade reshaped

21:04.070 --> 21:06.580
all immortal sects in the Central Plains.

21:06.920 --> 21:08.420
Immortal Lord, we welcome you back from seclusion!

21:08.600 --> 21:10.970
Immortal Lord, we welcome you back from seclusion!

21:11.640 --> 21:12.490
One day,

21:12.510 --> 21:15.530
a purple star crashed over the Xingzheng Hall.

21:15.880 --> 21:17.050
It was as large as a bushel

21:17.360 --> 21:19.940
and foretold the arrival of an immortal.

21:23.880 --> 21:26.180
Ji Tongzhou styled himself Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

21:26.600 --> 21:29.010
turning the Xingzheng Hall into the state guardian sect.

21:29.710 --> 21:31.290
He fought beside the Yue Emperor

21:31.710 --> 21:32.860
[Adult Ji Jingwu]
and vanquished every state,

21:33.440 --> 21:35.380
uniting the whole realm.

21:36.880 --> 21:39.530
The Wuyue Court under Deng Xiguang

21:40.070 --> 21:42.420
withdrew from the mortal realm,

21:43.070 --> 21:44.820
allowing the Xingzheng Hall to dominate.

21:48.960 --> 21:51.180
Ji Tongzhou sought to unify the immortal sects.

21:51.470 --> 21:54.420
He sent the Xuanhua Decree to the Mountain and Sea Sects.

21:54.880 --> 21:57.940
[Wanxian Sect]
Obey, or face destruction.

22:00.270 --> 22:01.580
Ji Tongzhou goes too far,

22:02.030 --> 22:03.660
ordering our sect to yield to the Xingzheng Hall.

22:04.270 --> 22:05.100
Over the past year,

22:05.750 --> 22:06.860
many sects refused to answer

22:06.880 --> 22:08.450
the summons of the Xuanhua Decree,

22:08.880 --> 22:10.900
only to be attacked and wiped out

22:11.270 --> 22:12.100
by the Xingzheng Hall.

22:14.710 --> 22:15.340
I heard

22:18.470 --> 22:19.620
the Dizang Sect has been destroyed as well.

22:22.960 --> 22:23.580
Jiao,

22:24.310 --> 22:25.380
I'm heading to the Xingzheng Hall

22:25.840 --> 22:26.900
to return the Xuanhua Decree.

22:27.510 --> 22:28.010
No,

22:28.270 --> 22:29.050
it's far too dangerous.

22:29.470 --> 22:31.340
Ji Tongzhou was once our fellow disciple.

22:31.840 --> 22:32.620
He won't harm me

22:32.960 --> 22:34.100
for old friendship's sake.

22:35.640 --> 22:36.290
Besides,

22:38.360 --> 22:39.340
we've had no word

22:39.750 --> 22:41.580
from Changyue and Ye since the Sea Calamity.

22:42.440 --> 22:43.450
I want to ask him about them.

22:44.230 --> 22:44.770
Fine.

22:45.550 --> 22:46.290
Stay alert.

22:46.750 --> 22:47.860
Don't push yourself

22:48.030 --> 22:48.900
if anything goes wrong.

22:59.160 --> 23:01.450
Your Highness's painting skills grow finer by the day.

24:04.070 --> 24:05.490
What's wrong? Unwell?

24:06.960 --> 24:09.580
Nothing. I think I ate something bad.

24:21.030 --> 24:21.530
Get rid of it.

24:24.030 --> 24:24.490
Your Highness,

24:25.470 --> 24:26.490
this is our child.

24:26.960 --> 24:27.490
I beg you.

24:28.030 --> 24:29.420
Spare the child, please.

24:34.600 --> 24:36.290
This must not happen again.

24:38.510 --> 24:39.660
Do not cling to foolish hopes.

24:40.750 --> 24:41.290
Your Highness,

24:42.230 --> 24:43.530
I can give up everything.

24:44.120 --> 24:44.820
I'm begging you.

24:45.360 --> 24:47.050
Spare our child, please.

25:25.160 --> 25:27.250
Are you dead or alive?

25:37.600 --> 25:38.050
Young lady.

25:40.920 --> 25:41.690
Miaoqing.

25:43.840 --> 25:44.690
He's utterly insane.

25:45.550 --> 25:46.690
He sees you as Lifei's substitute

25:46.710 --> 25:48.050
and won't even spare his own child.

25:50.640 --> 25:51.690
Let's confront him right now.

25:51.710 --> 25:52.290
No.

25:55.470 --> 25:56.050
Gelin,

25:56.960 --> 25:57.690
let go first.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.420
I know you mean well.

26:05.470 --> 26:06.820
Don't worry about me.

26:07.790 --> 26:10.340
I only want to give birth to this child.

26:11.360 --> 26:11.940
Nothing else

26:12.880 --> 26:13.620
matters.

26:22.160 --> 26:23.200
[Xuanhua Palace]

26:23.200 --> 26:24.580
Gelin, Lu Li,

26:25.070 --> 26:26.340
His Highness expected your arrival,

26:26.360 --> 26:27.140
and here you are.

26:29.400 --> 26:30.210
His Highness has stepped out,

26:30.400 --> 26:31.100
but he will return shortly.

26:31.470 --> 26:32.860
Please wait for him in his chamber.

26:37.640 --> 26:38.530
I don't know why

26:39.230 --> 26:41.340
this chamber reminds me of the academy.

26:42.200 --> 26:43.340
Looks just like our disciple lodgings, right?

26:48.750 --> 26:50.380
Tongzhou holds onto old memories.

26:56.880 --> 26:57.530
What's wrong?

27:00.470 --> 27:01.420
I can't explain it.

27:17.160 --> 27:17.860
What's wrong?

27:32.440 --> 27:33.010
No.

27:34.030 --> 27:34.690
It can't be true.

27:35.750 --> 27:36.490
It can't be true!

27:37.200 --> 27:38.820
Gelin, calm down.

27:39.160 --> 27:40.050
It's only a blade shoulder.

27:41.360 --> 27:43.210
The sword is the imperial token of Gaolu.

27:44.600 --> 27:46.250
Ye would never part with it.

27:52.270 --> 27:54.290
So it's the imperial token of Gaolu.

27:57.680 --> 27:59.770
No wonder even karmic fire could not burn it.

28:06.270 --> 28:07.490
- You killed them. - Gelin.

28:12.840 --> 28:13.580
Why?

28:14.750 --> 28:15.620
Tell me, why?

28:17.440 --> 28:19.050
They tried to stop me from killing Lei Xiuyuan.

28:21.270 --> 28:22.970
They brought it on themselves.

28:25.960 --> 28:26.450
Gelin,

28:27.360 --> 28:28.820
they died a decade ago.

28:38.510 --> 28:39.860
I treated all of you as friends,

28:42.960 --> 28:44.940
yet every one of you

28:44.960 --> 28:46.340
took that Demon Lord's side

28:47.920 --> 28:50.250
and betrayed me one after another.

28:53.070 --> 28:53.820
All of you

28:54.990 --> 28:56.180
deserve to die!

28:56.440 --> 28:57.820
Ji Tongzhou, you beast!

29:02.470 --> 29:03.380
I'll kill you!

29:15.710 --> 29:16.860
Take one more step forward,

29:17.360 --> 29:19.340
and she'll be consumed by karmic fire instantly.

29:25.600 --> 29:26.250
Ji Tongzhou,

29:27.120 --> 29:28.690
you let us find Ye Ye's blade shoulder

29:28.960 --> 29:29.770
and then grievously wounded Gelin.

29:30.640 --> 29:31.690
What exactly are you after?

29:35.310 --> 29:37.180
You're the Jiufeng Clan's leader, huh?

29:38.030 --> 29:40.420
I've heard you spirits have far-reaching intelligence

29:41.030 --> 29:43.010
and know every landform of the islands

29:43.030 --> 29:44.250
like the back of your hand.

29:45.360 --> 29:46.100
In six months,

29:47.710 --> 29:50.050
bring Jiang Lifei before me.

29:53.360 --> 29:54.250
If you fail,

29:55.360 --> 29:57.770
prepare to collect Gelin's ashes.

30:00.990 --> 30:01.820
Don't hurt her!

30:09.200 --> 30:09.940
I agree to your terms.

30:28.440 --> 30:29.140
Mark my words,

30:31.640 --> 30:32.730
only six months.

30:55.120 --> 30:56.340
A decade ago,

30:56.680 --> 30:58.970
the Divine Tree and Yecha sacrificed themselves

30:59.200 --> 31:00.290
to fend off the Sea Calamity.

31:00.640 --> 31:02.690
They ended the age-old karmic hatred,

31:02.710 --> 31:03.860
breaking the curse to be reborn.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.730
The Divine Tree's spirit meridians were completely shattered,

31:06.030 --> 31:07.690
and Yecha lost his supreme power.

31:07.990 --> 31:09.420
Though their cultivation faded drastically,

31:09.710 --> 31:10.940
they finally gained what they longed for.

31:12.070 --> 31:13.290
Lifei and the others have all left.

31:13.880 --> 31:15.290
Why are you still writing this tale?

31:16.160 --> 31:17.580
The story should have ended.

31:18.640 --> 31:20.010
Yet now, back in the Central Plains,

31:21.550 --> 31:23.140
we await a new ending.

31:24.550 --> 31:25.380
Years ago,

31:27.070 --> 31:28.490
when Qingcheng roamed overseas with me,

31:29.270 --> 31:30.900
he was worried about the Central Plains

31:32.510 --> 31:33.530
and insisted on returning.

31:35.360 --> 31:36.050
This time,

31:37.960 --> 31:40.100
there must be a different conclusion.

31:40.750 --> 31:43.210
But old karmic ties in the world remain.

31:43.600 --> 31:46.450
Ji Tongzhou holds Baili Gelin hostage,

31:46.920 --> 31:49.490
forcing Lu Li of the Jiufeng Clan to bring back the Divine Tree.

31:49.880 --> 31:51.180
Reluctant to leave her old friend,

31:51.790 --> 31:54.420
the Divine Tree travels home with Yecha.

32:01.790 --> 32:03.340
Lifei, don't grieve.

32:04.360 --> 32:05.380
Once you make a choice,

32:07.310 --> 32:08.340
you must bear its consequences.

32:10.550 --> 32:11.140
Xiuyuan.

32:11.360 --> 32:11.940
Lifei,

32:12.920 --> 32:13.900
my choice

32:14.840 --> 32:15.770
has always been you.

33:04.880 --> 33:05.420
Stand up.

33:05.440 --> 33:06.140
Thank you.

33:10.160 --> 33:10.970
Lifei.

33:22.880 --> 33:23.820
You're with child.

33:24.230 --> 33:25.450
Don't do heavy labor.

33:25.960 --> 33:27.140
Focus on safely giving birth to the baby.

33:28.160 --> 33:29.050
Lifei,

33:29.550 --> 33:30.820
do not blame His Highness.

33:31.880 --> 33:32.490
He...

33:35.880 --> 33:37.490
He killed my dearest friends

33:39.360 --> 33:40.420
and took Gelin captive.

33:45.960 --> 33:46.690
His Highness

33:47.710 --> 33:49.180
had no other choice.

33:49.880 --> 33:51.100
He never meant to hurt anyone.

33:52.120 --> 33:54.580
Does that excuse how he treated you?

33:57.790 --> 33:58.940
He's cold to me

33:59.960 --> 34:01.010
only because

34:02.470 --> 34:03.900
I can never be you.

34:05.200 --> 34:06.250
You'll never be me.

34:06.470 --> 34:07.420
You belong to yourself.

34:07.710 --> 34:08.820
You've sacrificed so much for him.

34:09.160 --> 34:10.820
He ought to cherish and treat you well,

34:11.120 --> 34:11.860
instead of...

34:11.880 --> 34:12.700
I don't blame him.

34:14.510 --> 34:15.490
I chose this willingly.

34:18.070 --> 34:19.610
I have no spirit energy

34:19.630 --> 34:20.570
to heal your wounds.

34:23.630 --> 34:25.650
Keep this money and protective talismans

34:26.470 --> 34:27.530
to safeguard yourself.

34:28.400 --> 34:29.130
Lifei,

34:30.110 --> 34:32.570
you're going to see His Highness, right?

34:34.670 --> 34:35.900
Take good care of yourself

34:36.360 --> 34:37.050
and your child.

34:42.440 --> 34:43.300
What are your odds?

34:48.070 --> 34:49.900
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Highness.

34:56.360 --> 34:57.530
Ji Tongzhou is using Gelin as bait,

34:57.840 --> 34:58.740
all to lure you here.

34:58.880 --> 34:59.700
If you go over there

34:59.800 --> 35:00.650
and he sees through your disguise...

35:02.320 --> 35:03.050
It won't happen.

35:03.880 --> 35:05.820
I've never failed at tricking anyone.

35:06.280 --> 35:06.780
No way.

35:07.510 --> 35:08.450
Ji Tongzhou is far too shrewd to be fooled.

35:10.590 --> 35:12.130
I know this is pulling chestnuts out of the fire,

35:12.670 --> 35:14.900
yet we have no other options right now.

35:15.720 --> 35:16.490
Don't worry.

35:17.030 --> 35:18.740
I'll sneak in to find out where Gelin is.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.090
I'll avoid him at all costs if I can.

35:20.470 --> 35:21.090
Nothing will go wrong.

35:21.590 --> 35:22.340
I'm coming with you.

35:23.070 --> 35:23.530
You...

35:23.990 --> 35:24.610
You said

35:25.360 --> 35:25.970
nothing would go wrong.

35:28.630 --> 35:30.260
It's settled then.

35:40.110 --> 35:42.010
Miaoqing, you're back!

35:43.320 --> 35:43.970
Mr. Zhao.

35:44.630 --> 35:45.860
It's been ages. Where have you been?

35:46.630 --> 35:47.380
While you were gone,

35:47.400 --> 35:48.780
His Highness was in a bad mood every day.

35:49.280 --> 35:50.490
We all hoped you'd return soon.

35:51.240 --> 35:52.740
I just wandered around.

35:53.070 --> 35:54.340
I've missed His Highness deeply, too.

35:55.800 --> 35:57.420
I heard Miss Baili visited

35:57.440 --> 35:58.860
His Highness the other day,

35:59.190 --> 36:01.050
and they seemed to argue.

36:01.440 --> 36:02.450
Did His Highness get hurt?

36:02.920 --> 36:04.090
She's no match for him.

36:04.760 --> 36:05.820
He locked her up long ago.

36:05.990 --> 36:06.700
Where is she being locked?

36:07.190 --> 36:07.700
She is...

36:12.630 --> 36:13.260
Miaoqing,

36:14.440 --> 36:15.700
why bother yourself with this?

36:19.550 --> 36:19.940
Who's there?

36:21.720 --> 36:22.820
This Truth-Revealing Talisman

36:23.320 --> 36:25.450
will make us safe and sound.

36:48.240 --> 36:48.780
Gelin!

36:50.670 --> 36:51.340
Miaoqing.

36:52.110 --> 36:52.970
Stand back.

37:00.590 --> 37:01.380
Lifei,

37:02.670 --> 37:03.420
you've come back.

37:12.960 --> 37:13.530
Yes.

37:14.670 --> 37:15.740
She's finally returned.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.700
Welcome home.

37:21.880 --> 37:22.740
Ji Tongzhou,

37:23.720 --> 37:24.570
you beast!

37:39.960 --> 37:41.010
It's been a decade.

37:42.030 --> 37:43.420
I've waited for this moment.

37:44.840 --> 37:46.050
Let's hold our wedding ceremony anew.

37:46.880 --> 37:47.530
This time,

37:47.800 --> 37:48.740
no one will ever tear you

37:48.760 --> 37:49.900
away from me.

37:51.030 --> 37:52.420
We can stay together forever.

37:53.400 --> 37:54.010
That can't be.

37:54.760 --> 37:56.170
Xiuyuan and I are married.

37:57.840 --> 37:58.610
What did you say?

37:59.800 --> 38:01.970
She said we're married. Can't you understand?

38:04.440 --> 38:04.940
Lifei.

38:09.470 --> 38:10.650
Lei Xiuyuan!

38:14.070 --> 38:15.170
Ji Tongzhou!

38:19.840 --> 38:20.340
Watch out!

38:22.070 --> 38:22.490
Run!

38:28.960 --> 38:30.130
Why not unleash your Yecha power?

38:30.840 --> 38:31.780
You're the Demon Lord.

38:32.960 --> 38:34.490
Don't think the world will accept you

38:35.110 --> 38:36.300
just because you ended the Sea Calamity.

38:36.920 --> 38:38.010
The Sea Calamity arose

38:38.320 --> 38:39.380
precisely because of you.

38:40.400 --> 38:41.610
You're wrong.

38:42.960 --> 38:44.300
It was born from your own greed.

38:44.920 --> 38:46.380
The Divine Tree never fell in love with your ancestor.

38:47.320 --> 38:48.450
He coveted the Divine Tree's power,

38:48.470 --> 38:49.340
hoping to seize it for himself.

38:50.470 --> 38:51.530
[Ancestor of the Ji clan]
When he failed,

38:51.990 --> 38:52.970
he colluded with the immortal sects

38:53.400 --> 38:54.650
to ambush her in the East Sea,

38:54.840 --> 38:55.570
costing her life.

38:56.360 --> 38:57.300
The ancient gods were furious

38:57.840 --> 38:59.940
and unleashed the Sea Calamity to punish you all.

39:51.630 --> 39:52.420
You're lying!

39:53.440 --> 39:54.780
Had your ancestor not absorbed

39:55.630 --> 39:56.170
the Divine Tree's power,

39:56.190 --> 39:57.700
how could he have forged the Xuanhua Karmic Fire?

39:58.760 --> 40:01.420
Tongzhou, you know better than anyone

40:01.670 --> 40:03.170
what is required to master the karmic fire.

40:07.070 --> 40:08.170
The Sea Calamity is long gone.

40:09.470 --> 40:10.970
It's time to let go of your obsession.

40:17.150 --> 40:18.300
You have attained an immortal physique,

40:19.150 --> 40:20.450
and we stand no match for you.

40:21.320 --> 40:22.740
Why can't you let this go?

40:25.360 --> 40:26.220
Let go?

40:27.720 --> 40:29.010
How could I ever let go?

40:29.800 --> 40:31.340
If you had not stubbornly gone your own way

40:31.990 --> 40:33.130
and left me all alone,

40:34.110 --> 40:35.650
the Sea Calamity would never have happened.

40:36.030 --> 40:38.380
Ye Ye and Changyue would still be alive.

40:39.110 --> 40:40.260
It is all your fault.

40:40.630 --> 40:42.380
Because you chose Yecha.

40:43.030 --> 40:43.820
Ji Tongzhou,

40:44.840 --> 40:45.650
enough of your madness.

40:46.840 --> 40:47.970
All the slaughter is of your own making,

40:48.550 --> 40:49.900
but you shift the blame to others.

40:50.630 --> 40:52.220
How can you face Ye Ye and the rest?

40:53.880 --> 40:54.610
Mad?

40:58.720 --> 41:01.940
I only regret I didn't lose my mind sooner.

41:08.320 --> 41:09.860
Your Highness, stop,

41:10.070 --> 41:11.300
or you will live to regret it.

41:11.470 --> 41:12.860
Even you betrayed me, too!

41:13.470 --> 41:13.970
Get lost!

41:30.240 --> 41:30.820
Xiuyuan!

41:44.030 --> 41:45.530
Uncle, save me!

41:46.840 --> 41:47.260
Release them,

41:47.920 --> 41:48.740
or I'll kill him.

41:51.150 --> 41:51.610
Uncle,

41:52.550 --> 41:53.820
Lifei once saved my life

41:54.280 --> 41:55.050
and helped the Yue State.

41:55.800 --> 41:56.490
Spare them.

41:57.190 --> 41:58.170
Let there be no more killing.

41:58.720 --> 41:59.740
Let them leave.

41:59.880 --> 42:00.490
Silence!

42:01.440 --> 42:02.380
With such cowardice,

42:02.960 --> 42:04.570
how will you guard the Yue State's realm?

42:21.240 --> 42:21.820
Xiuyuan!

42:42.050 --> 42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.360 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
